### =============================================
### Veltrix API - Tests Organisation
### =============================================

@base_url = http://localhost:8000/api/v1
@token = REMPLACER_PAR_TON_TOKEN

### 1. Mon organisation
GET {{base_url}}/organizations/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 2. Statistiques de mon organisation
GET {{base_url}}/organizations/me/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 3. Liste agents filtree - online seulement
GET {{base_url}}/agents?status=online
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 4. Liste agents filtree - pending
GET {{base_url}}/agents?status=pending
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 5. Filtre statut invalide -> 400 standardise
GET {{base_url}}/agents?status=invalid_status
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### 6. Agent inexistant -> 404 standardise
GET {{base_url}}/agents/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
